{"tid":2288747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴馬拒入拜登内閣「米歇爾會離開我」","createTime":"2020-11-16T17:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T08:00:51.000Z","uid":63543,"like":16,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1350fc7669f02ff7838f0c400cf320427522b1","tid":2288747,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"美國大選結果幾乎塵埃落定，民主黨總統候選人拜登料勝出美國大選，但美國總統特朗普尚未承認落敗。拜登正籌組内閣，英媒早前指拜登有意委任奧巴馬出任駐英國大使。但奧巴馬接受美媒訪問時表示不會考慮入拜登内閣，因害怕妻子米歇爾會離開自己。<br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬（Barack Obama）的回憶錄《A Promised Land》將於周二（17日）出版，記錄他任美國參議院議員和第一個總統任期的事跡。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬周日（15日）接受哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）訪問時，被問及將如何協助拜登（Joe Biden）。奧巴馬表示拜登不需要自己的建議，又指自己不會考慮突然在白宮工作（not planning to suddenly work on the White House staff or something.）。<br />\n<br />\n主持追問奧巴馬會否考慮進入拜登内閣，奧巴馬表示：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">&ldquo;有些事情我不會做，因為米歇爾會離開我。她會說：「甚麼？你在做甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n（There are some things I would not be doing because Michelle would leave me. She&rsquo;d be like, what? You&rsquo;re doing what?）&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n據悉，奧巴馬在即將出版的新書也有提到，他在參議院及白宮迅速崛起，對他與妻子米歇爾的婚姻，以及與兩名女兒的家庭生活有何意義。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬指他為了政治生涯而未能兼顧家庭，導致妻子米歇爾為免離開兩名女兒太長時間，不止一次放棄發展其法律事業的機會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，奧巴馬早前接受美國名嘴奧花雲費（Oprah Winfrey）的訪問，也有提及與妻子米歇爾的相處之道。奧巴馬形容他和妻子擅長溝通交流，兩人永遠都會保持愛的基礎和彼此尊重，及凡事考慮女兒為先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2804027/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%86%85%E9%96%A3%E3%80%8C%E7%B1%B3%E6%AD%87%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2804027%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2586%2585%25E9%2596%25A3%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E6%25AD%2587%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%2591%25E3%2580%258D&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu6y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=5aee683d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2804027/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%86%85%E9%96%A3%E3%80%8C%E7%B1%B3%E6%AD%87%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n個女俾獵人食完，再跟一齊去索k<br />\n個老母幾左膠大愛都包容唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f520d5b9b870783777d017ea192a80273e808e","tid":2288747,"uid":181088,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02dc754d3caaa863defe00bba0aff9fe3086202","tid":2288747,"uid":56624,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"要被以前嘅下屬點返轉頭梗係唔制"},{"pid":"b00c15b2616fee63c9c2e66ac00f1d260f40c119","tid":2288747,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國大選結果幾乎塵埃落定，民主黨總統候選人拜登料勝出美國大選</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37e3f39f5731e481b1d166a8cc0f9c422bec751","tid":2288747,"uid":65289,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導致妻子米歇爾為免離開兩名女兒太長時間，不止一次放棄發展其法律事業的機會。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話自己睇到咁實個女結果係群埋 hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2c47ea98b8ddc74d5a5417fcb3d05c0b95d74d","tid":2288747,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11f520d5b9b870783777d017ea192a80273e808e","tid":2288747,"uid":181088,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":